               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430612-name-1445" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1445" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1445" type="surname" value="HASTINGS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1445" type="given" value="FRANCES SOPHIA"></interp>FRANCES SOPHIA HASTINGS</persName>
                  </hi>. I am single, and live in the Quadrant, in Regent-street. The prisoner was in my service for ten or eleven weeks, up to about the 1st of June—I discharged her—about a fortnight before that I had missed a pair of boots and two shifts—I accused her of taking them, she denied it—on the 8th of June I missed a cloak, and a handkerchief—this cloak, handkerchief, and two shifts are mine, and what I missed—here are two other shifts which I did not miss, but I found them at the pawnbrokers.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430612-name-1446" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1446" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1446" type="surname" value="WYNESS"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18430612-name-1446" type="given" value="ANDREW"></interp>ANDREW WYNESS</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable D</hi> 43.) I took the prisoner on the 8th of June—I went with her to No. 3, Foley-street, I there saw her looking at some duplicates which were in her hand—she put them into her pocket—I asked her to give me them—she was very abusive, and marched about the room and would not hear what I had got to say—I told a lady in the room to tell the prisoner to give them to me, but she would not—I then took her hands and called in the landlady, who took the tickets from her pocket—these are them.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18430612-name-1447" type="witnessName">
