                  </hi>. I am shopman to Mr. Fleming, a pawnbroker. I pro<lb></lb>duce a cloak and a handkerchief pawned by the prisoner on the 16th of May—I produce two shifts, pawned on the 1st of May by a man—the tickets pro<lb></lb>duced by the officer were given for them.</p>
               <p>
